🤗Saturday morning #hometour!

💁🏻‍♂️You’ll at least want to go inside to check out that staircase (🙆🏻‍♂️?!) I mean, this entire #lakehouse is #modern, but the stairs are... just wow!
.
#lakemichigan #modernhome by @northworks_architects @karamanndesign 📸: @reagentaylor
.
🙋🏻‍♂️Hi! Hope you enjoyed the #hometour!
